data.description: Bring your design eye! This home has had major updates including roof, gutters, insulation, windows, electrical, minisplit, driveway, steps, walkway, patio, and garage! This home has a great location to walk to restaurants and shopping. The home is zoned BB commercial perfect for running your business! The classic white A frame colonial sits on a beautiful flat lot on a cul de sac. The detached garage with foam insulation has business potential. The screened porch and patio is perfect for those summer nights to gather and unwind. The freshly painted living and dining rooms offer hardwoods and high ceilings. The country kitchen has a great view overlooking the yard and direct driveway access. The first floor has a bedroom or office option and the 3 rooms on the second level have great potential as bedrooms, office space, or future 2nd bath! Make this home your own in the sought after community of Westborough with top notch schools and commuter access to the Train-30-9-495-90!
